        "rendered": "Using the File Field"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "<h2>Basic Setup</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a new Field Group</li>\n<li>Add a File field</li>\n<li>Configure options:\n<ul>\n<li>Set allowed file types</li>\n<li>Configure size limits</li>\n<li>Choose library restriction</li>\n<li>Set return format</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Common Use Cases</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Document Management\n<ul>\n<li>PDF uploads</li>\n<li>Document attachments</li>\n<li>Resource libraries</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Media Handling\n<ul>\n<li>Download files</li>\n<li>Asset management</li>\n<li>Resource linking</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Tips</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Restrict file types appropriately</li>\n<li>Set reasonable size limits</li>\n<li>Consider storage implications</li>\n<li>Use clear preview options</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
